# id: TransportGetRollupJobAction -> static boolean stateHasRollupJobs(GetRollupJobsAction.Request request, ClusterState state)
commentText: Check to see if the PersistentTask's cluster state contains the rollup job(s) we are interested in
codeText: static boolean stateHasRollupJobs(GetRollupJobsAction.Request request, ClusterState state) {_        boolean hasRollupJobs = false__        PersistentTasksCustomMetaData pTasksMeta = state.getMetaData().custom(PersistentTasksCustomMetaData.TYPE)___        if (pTasksMeta != null) {_            _            _            if (request.getId().equals(MetaData.ALL)) {_                hasRollupJobs = pTasksMeta.tasks()_                        .stream()_                        .anyMatch(persistentTask -> persistentTask.getTaskName().equals(RollupField.TASK_NAME))___            } else if (pTasksMeta.getTask(request.getId()) != null) {_                _                hasRollupJobs = true__            }_        }_        return hasRollupJobs__    }
